//Program to check profit, loss or nothing, and what is the amount
int main()
{
    int sp,pp,a;
    printf("\n enter the purchase price and selling price:");
    scanf("%d%d",&pp,&sp);
    a=sp-pp;
    if (a<0)
        printf("\n loss=%d",a*(-1));
    else if(a>0)
        printf("\n profit=%d",a);
    else
        printf("\n neither profit nor loss");
}

Output:
enter the purchase price and selling price:
45
87

 profit=42

Reference:https://funcodepro.blogspot.com/2018/12/how-to-know-whether-it-is-profit-or.html
